name: Trip into calligraphy world
description: This work combined two styles, street calligraphy and digital art. Showing the transition to a new era of creativity. Work was done in the first collaboration project NFT256  Description 256 Artist. 256 Works. 7555 Hours. The final result was be a secret for everyone. No one knew how the art would look like. Until now. Artists from different disciplines from all over the world did it together. It's an amazing experience and the biggest collaboration in NFT history.You’ll also get an extra card. Just contact me
